{"tid":1096731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嗜辣社工猝亡 五口家失支柱徬徨","createTime":"2019-04-08T02:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T03:28:32.000Z","uid":56881,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"16a3845f75ad803e383fef1366369fd250995ef5","tid":1096731,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%97%9C%E8%BE%A3%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%8C%9D%E4%BA%A1-%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%9F%B1%E5%BE%AC%E5%BE%A8-222657279.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2597%259C%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%258C%259D%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%259F%25B1%25E5%25BE%25AC%25E5%25BE%25A8-222657279.html&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a1833981\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%97%9C%E8%BE%A3%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%8C%9D%E4%BA%A1-%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%9F%B1%E5%BE%AC%E5%BE%A8-222657279.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/g2D.Am6wUYZPp5MV3wNSLA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDI4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/f6581f180fc2d11188f755d76b38bcd0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fg2D.Am6wUYZPp5MV3wNSLA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDI4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ff6581f180fc2d11188f755d76b38bcd0&h=977a511c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主送院後不治，遺下妻女及父母。<br />\n<br />\n嗜辣壯年社工，日前品嘗「麻辣鍋」後感胃痛，曾前往求醫卻「唔斷尾」，期間，他腰部亦出現劇痛，至前晚他在柴灣住所突然暈倒，惜送院後不治，遺下妻女及年邁父母，家庭頓失經濟支柱，遺孀坦言大感徬徨。有醫生指胃部不適一般不會短時間致命，估計事主猝死原因或涉心臟毛病。<br />\n<br />\n猝死男子陳家慶（卅六歲），洋名Steven。據悉，陳在一一年結婚，與姓洪（卅二歲）妻子育有六歲女兒，陳與父母及妻女共五人。據了解，陳是註冊社工，在新界區一間社福機構工作，負責幫助來港居住的新移民融入社會。陳妻任職幼稚園教師。據悉，陳工作勤奮，但仍不時抽空與妻女遊山玩水。<br />\n<br />\n曾求診「唔斷尾」 家中突暈倒<br />\n消息指，陳為「嗜辣一族」，約一星期前與友人吃麻辣火鍋後胃部突感不適。陳求診後「好番好多」，星期一及二如常上班，周三又感腰痛，僅上班半天。翌日痛楚減輕，陳照常上班，惟周五再感腰痛，於周六往骨科醫生求診，陳向家人透露稱：「好好多吧！」<br />\n<br />\n直至前晚九時許，陳在家晚飯後欣賞電視節目，期間，突感胃部劇痛，未幾暈倒，妻子見狀報警，惜送院搶救不治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食辣食到咁"},{"pid":"6402a177568cddb7cf04ffef723e991e90431f47","tid":1096731,"uid":37733,"like":4,"dislike":38,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"是註冊社工，在新界區一間社福機構工作，負責幫助來港居住的新移民融入社會。<br />\n<br />\n一個好人 咁就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a57c632670f7db6f638640d9bb9724c1aca33d","tid":1096731,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:05:02.000Z","msg":"go 大灣區"},{"pid":"d6c91dd53cff7cdf9335f6d21c1c0c9b1acfd162","tid":1096731,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"6402a177568cddb7cf04ffef723e991e90431f47","tid":1096731,"uid":37733,"like":4,"dislike":38,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"是註冊社工，在新界區一間社福機構工作，負責幫助來港居住的新移民融入社會。<br />\n<br />\n一個好人 咁就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"難得的好人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf89e0ca6078cc55a443c2b75486fbda25b0e32c","tid":1096731,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"e157bb62974e637bf084f4265e39366637ad115b","tid":1096731,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"叫党養佢，或者佢幫過咁多新移民叫佢地幫返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e36045ead001a8869e73931eb329cb7f076234e","tid":1096731,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6c91dd53cff7cdf9335f6d21c1c0c9b1acfd162","tid":1096731,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"6402a177568cddb7cf04ffef723e991e90431f47","tid":109673